title: Modest Mouse CD Cover typefaces?
content:
Was curious about all the fonts that were uded on this CD cover.  
Anyone know what any of these fonts are?

Thanks.

author: tomjonesrocks

comments.content: Actually — it looks like I found most of the fonts for this — “Dead” (Linotype Macbeth) and “Before the Ship” (Banque Gothique RR Bold Extra Condensed) and found some fonts similar for “Even Sank” and “We Were”.
